headline: Interpublic (IPG) Reports Q3 Earnings: What Key Metrics Have to Say
summary: The headline numbers for Interpublic (IPG) give insight into how the company performed in the quarter ended September 2025, but it may be worthwhile to compare some of its key metrics to Wall Street estimates and the year-ago actuals.
